- Join Channel:
  . public channel are display with number of users inside
  . display a lock for protected channel and ask for password
  . join by channel name for private channels
- Channel settings
  MEMBERS
  . invite other user
  ADMINS: 
  . ban / mute other users if admin
  CREATOR
  . delete channel
  . rename channel
- Chat notification:
  . Invites / Bans / Mute

Optionnal:
  . Notification on new messages
